From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Tue, 3 Feb 2026 00:16:14 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: dts: cix: Add Orange Pi 6 Plus device tree

Add board DTS for the Orange Pi 6 Plus (CIX Sky1 SoC), adapted from
community contribution (PR #1 by Entrpi). Uses the shared sky1.dtsi
instead of a duplicated SoC DTSI.

Nodes referencing labels not present in sky1.dtsi (pwm2, pwm3,
cache_exception) are replaced with comments preserving the board
hardware documentation.

Also fix missing #sound-dai-cells on ipb_hda node in sky1.dtsi which
caused a dtc warning for any board enabling HDA audio.
